result.markdown: --- title: "Download final data" format: html: code-tools: false toc: false --- The cleaned data is available in three formats: - CSV file for any program - `.rds` file for R (load with `df <- readRDS("weekly_panel.rds")`) - `.dta` file for Stata (load with `use "weekly_panel.dta"`) ## Weekly data {{< fa table >}}  weekly_panel.csv   {{< fa brands r-project >}}  weekly_panel.rds   {{< fa table-cells >}}  weekly_panel.dta ## Quarterly data {{< fa table >}}  quarterly_panel.csv   {{< fa brands r-project >}}  quarterly_panel.rds   {{< fa table-cells >}}  quarterly_panel.dta
